  "text": "However, this new imaging method is entirely different from existing techniques and therefore must be validated. There are many reports demonstrating an excellent correlation between ex vivo FCM images and histopathologic analysis for nonmelanoma skin cancer. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] However, none have reported a structured description of FCM features for BCCs nor validated truthful criteria to differentiate it from the surrounding dermis and adnexal structures .",
